        {
            "text": "During an epidemiologic screening of patients with C. diffi cile infection in a university hospital in Chile, we analyzed all stool samples of patients with suspected C. diffi cile infection during a 5-month period (June-November 2011). Two cases of C. diffi cile infection were associated with ribotype 027.",
